          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "机，怎比这隆中清闲自在，安然逍遥，好不快乐人也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有山人居南阳何等清静，"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "每日里无非是乐把田耕。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "闷倦时到山后听鸟啼鸣；"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "酒醒来焚名香抚琴吹笙；"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "酷暑天摇羽扇阵阵风清。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "往来的石广元、公威、州平。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老白鹤守门户夜夜听更。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那边厢挂的是宝剑七星。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "并未曾观看那文史五经。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "取过了圣贤书细看分明。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为王家争名利俱丧幽冥。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有几个为武将阵前倾生。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "离乱世作忠臣哪有收成？"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "斩杀的全是那忠烈公卿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贪什么名和利富贵功名。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫童儿焚名香抚琴一听。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "童儿！"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "闲来时在山前观看美景"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "酒醉后发狂歌信口吟咏"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "寒冬夜着鹤氅纶巾齐整"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我腹中怀韬略神机妙用"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小猿猴常叩户献桃相庆"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "桌案上摆的是琴棋古镜"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这几日同诸友闲谈古洞"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "掸灰尘来至在交椅坐定"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "前三皇后五帝许多贤圣"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有几个为文官心机尽用"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "太平年君待臣颇知敬重"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "满朝中尽是些贼臣奸佞"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看起来倒不如埋名隐姓"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看古书不由我心神不定"
        },
        {
          "character": "童儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "焚香伺候！山人要操琴一曲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（徐庶上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "实可叹同胞弟一旦丧命，"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恨曹贼将老母诳进曹营。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "拜山人为参谋言必听从。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "别皇叔为的是母子之情。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "临行时荐举了谋士二人："
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如得一便可作汉室重臣。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "又只见卧龙岗雾气腾腾。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "近看时悬瀑布流水传声。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有苍松和翠柏四季长青。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "又只见日将午分外光明。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我只得在门外侧耳细听。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（诸葛亮抚琴。〖夜深沉〗。诸葛亮忽惊。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正抚琴忽然间音调变动，"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想必有知音客门外窃听。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "下草亭出门来观看动静"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤弟，愚兄在此。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "见仁兄走向前施礼相迎。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "仁兄请！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（徐庶进门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请坐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不知仁兄驾到，未曾远迎，望乞恕罪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂敢！少问金安，贤弟海涵！"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好说。许久未会，兄往何处去了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兄闻刘表名扬八郡，招贤纳士。兄至荆州，见他善善而不能进，恶恶而不能退，"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "徒有虚名，是以见机而退。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刘景升乃无用之人，兄长提他作甚？"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "愚兄又至新野，多蒙皇叔拜为参谋，礼贤下士，言听计从，乃仁德之主也。可"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恨曹贼将愚兄老母诳至许昌，屡欲加害，多亏程昱搭救。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兄长不去，伯母安然无事。兄至曹营，伯母倘有不测，岂不悔之晚也？"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你我所见相同。怎奈母子天性，无可如何！愚兄临行，已将贤弟荐于皇叔，万"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "望出山，大展奇才，辅佐汉室，落得流芳千古，青史留名，不愧贤弟胸中之志，"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "平生所学也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎！你去便去，荐我作甚？你真真多此一举！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎，贤弟呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一句话说得我口呆目瞪，"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不由人耳发赤满面通红。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听愚兄表一表肺腑之情："
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "献帝爷称皇叔叙谱传宗；"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "与关、张结昆仲义气相同。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一心要灭群寇扶汉中兴；"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众百姓担酒浆俱把他迎；"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "虎牢关战吕布四海扬名；"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "投刘表守新野大运未通；"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有一朝时运至平地雷鸣。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兴汉室灭孙、曹名就功成。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂不怕高明士笑我弟兄！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "无奈何对贤弟把话告禀"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刘玄德居楼桑炎汉正统"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "自幼儿在原郡品高术正"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在桃园起义兵人人钦敬"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "数百人挡住了千万贼众"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "立功劳得授了平原县令"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "论仁义比尧"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "舜"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "禹"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "汤平等"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "并非是池中物守拙无用"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "望贤弟辅佐他纵横驰骋"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你若是在茅庐安然清静"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "徐仁兄你心中名利甚重，"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小弟我并不想富贵功名。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎奈他并无有辅助英雄。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刘玄德汉宗亲根基虽正"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "论武将有关、张、赵云猛勇，"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "文士呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有糜竺和靡芳、孙乾、简雍。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "论关、张和子龙皆可用命，"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "论文官全都是白面书生。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "曹孟德、孙仲谋虽然强胜，"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "论争战怎比得桃园英雄？"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "关云长过五关四海扬名。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "当阳桥一声吼曹贼胆惊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "金锁阵破袁绍百万雄兵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一个个有万夫不当之勇"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "张翼德他生来虎豹之性"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赵子龙战场上威风凛凛"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "桃园中一个个旗开得胜，"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兄去后何人能遣将用兵？"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "荐贤弟为的是汉室为重，"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万望你扶皇叔早把功成。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咱二人暗通信共扫奸雄。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兄在曹弟在汉两相呼应"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老兄长说的是治国之政，"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "弟本是闲散人不堪用兵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "徐元直百般的好言相请，"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他那里只当作耳旁风声。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有一派古圣贤贤弟细听："
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他也曾保江山万古留名。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姜子牙兴周朝八百余冬。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小乐毅下齐国七十余城。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "全凭着小韩信、张良、陈平；"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "云台观廿八将辅保江洪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "平曹操扫孙权大展奇能。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "封妻子荫儿孙光耀门庭。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "无奈何近前来施礼告禀"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "昔日里有伊尹可称贤圣"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "周文王夜得兆飞熊入梦"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "苏季子说六国相印独领"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "汉高祖逼霸王乌江丧命"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "汉光武被困在南阳路径"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "望贤弟早下山兵将来统"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "荣宗祖扬名声何等有幸"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "劝兄长你不必古人比定，"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这一般栋梁材哪个善终？"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杀彭越斩韩信未央宫中；"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "云台观众将军俱丧残生。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "功不就名不成劳而无功。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小弟我只当作耳边狂风。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "也免得老伯母双目盼红。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你就说诸葛亮少问安宁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "无奈何近前来施礼告禀"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "昔日里有伊尹可称贤圣"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "周文王夜得兆飞熊入梦"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "苏季子说六国相印独领"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "汉高祖逼霸王乌江丧命"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "汉光武被困在南阳路径"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "望贤弟早下山兵将来统"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "荣宗祖扬名声何等有幸"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恕不送兄，另请高明。请吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（诸葛亮下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "诸葛亮性情傲言语强胜，"
        }
      ],
